        <h2 id="about-he-heading" class="font-serif text-aiq-3xl font-normal tracking-aiq-tight text-aiq-fg-primary mb-aiq-xl mt-0">
          What HackerEarth is known for.
        </h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-aiq-2xl">
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-serif text-aiq-xl font-normal tracking-aiq-tight text-aiq-fg-primary mb-aiq-sm mt-0">Developer community at scale.</h3>
            <p class="font-sans text-aiq-md text-aiq-fg-secondary leading-relaxed m-0">
              HackerEarth has built one of the largest developer communities in India — 10M+ registered developers. Its hackathon and hiring-challenge product lets companies source candidates beyond their existing applicant pool.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-serif text-aiq-xl font-normal tracking-aiq-tight text-aiq-fg-primary mb-aiq-sm mt-0">Deep technical question library.</h3>
