              With 36,000+ questions covering 1,000+ skills across 100+ job roles and 40+ programming languages, HackerEarth's content library is one of the broadest available for technical hiring.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-serif text-aiq-xl font-normal tracking-aiq-tight text-aiq-fg-primary mb-aiq-sm mt-0">End-to-end developer lifecycle.</h3>
            <p class="font-sans text-aiq-md text-aiq-fg-secondary leading-relaxed m-0">
              HackerEarth for Enterprises spans sourcing, screening, interviewing, and upskilling — positioning it as a full developer talent management platform rather than a point-solution for assessments.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-serif text-aiq-xl font-normal tracking-aiq-tight text-aiq-fg-primary mb-aiq-sm mt-0">AI-assisted interviews.</h3>
            <p class="font-sans text-aiq-md text-aiq-fg-secondary leading-relaxed m-0">
