            <p class="font-mono text-aiq-xs text-aiq-fg-muted tracking-aiq-mono uppercase mb-aiq-sm mt-0 font-medium">HackerEarth may suit you if…</p>
            <ul class="font-sans text-aiq-md text-aiq-fg-secondary leading-relaxed m-0 p-0 list-none flex flex-col gap-aiq-sm">
              <li class="flex gap-aiq-sm"><span class="text-aiq-fg-muted flex-shrink-0">—</span><span>Sourcing candidates through hackathons and public hiring challenges is part of your strategy.</span></li>
              <li class="flex gap-aiq-sm"><span class="text-aiq-fg-muted flex-shrink-0">—</span><span>You want access to a pre-screened developer community as a sourcing channel alongside your own pipeline.</span></li>
              <li class="flex gap-aiq-sm"><span class="text-aiq-fg-muted flex-shrink-0">—</span><span>You need a very large question library spanning 40+ languages and 1,000+ skills out of the box.</span></li>
              <li class="flex gap-aiq-sm"><span class="text-aiq-fg-muted flex-shrink-0">—</span><span>AI-native live interview tooling is a priority alongside asynchronous assessments.</span></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-aiq-bg-base border border-aiq-border rounded-aiq-lg p-aiq-xl">
            <p class="font-mono text-aiq-xs text-aiq-accent tracking-aiq-mono uppercase mb-aiq-sm mt-0 font-medium">AssessIQ may suit you if…</p>
            <ul class="font-sans text-aiq-md text-aiq-fg-secondary leading-relaxed m-0 p-0 list-none flex flex-col gap-aiq-sm">
