              <li class="flex gap-aiq-sm"><span class="text-aiq-accent flex-shrink-0">—</span><span>Structured scoring with per-answer rationale and audit trails matters for your hiring reviews or compliance.</span></li>
              <li class="flex gap-aiq-sm"><span class="text-aiq-accent flex-shrink-0">—</span><span>You are running bulk hiring across multiple roles and need a lean admin workflow without community-management overhead.</span></li>
              <li class="flex gap-aiq-sm"><span class="text-aiq-accent flex-shrink-0">—</span><span>India-first pricing and local data residency are requirements.</span></li>
