          <p class="font-sans text-aiq-md text-aiq-fg-secondary leading-relaxed m-0">
            HackerEarth is a technical assessment and developer hiring platform founded in Bengaluru, India. It combines coding assessments (40+ programming languages, 36,000+ question library) with a large developer community (10M+ registered developers) and hackathon/hiring-challenge tools. Enterprises use it to source, screen, and interview developer talent.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-b border-aiq-border pb-aiq-xl">
          <h3 class="font-serif text-aiq-xl font-normal tracking-aiq-tight text-aiq-fg-primary mb-aiq-sm mt-0">How does AssessIQ differ from HackerEarth?</h3>
